      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_6670087356363141100.png",
                "id": "talent59138",
                "key": "Electro Crystal Projection",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro Crystal Projection"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span> and then separately performs \"<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prepare Skill</span>\" for <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Rock-Paper-Scissors Combo: Scissors</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Rock-Paper-Scissors Combo: Pape</span>r.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Rock-Paper-Scissors Combo: Scissors</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>, then performs \"<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Prepare Skill</span>\" for <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Rock-Paper-Scissors Combo: Paper</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Rock-Paper-Scissors Combo: Paper</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/0e809f0cd877c453ef4eb86e7d1b8cbf_4186100597304632919.png",
                "id": "talent68920",
                "key": "Rock-Paper-Scissors Combo",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rock-Paper-Scissors Combo"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>, summoning <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Chains of Warding Thunder</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/4baa599d0dc30449e310756e218280e2_211322735167807336.png",
                "id": "talent9544",
                "key": "Lightning Lockdown",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lightning Lockdown"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains an <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystal Core</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Electro Crystal Core</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When the character to which this is attached would be defeated</span>: Remove this effect, ensure the character <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">will not be defeated</span>, and heal them to 1 HP.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Immunity to Defeat</span></strong></p><p>Certain effects will grant characters an<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> immunity to being defeated</span> when their HP hits 0, and will heal them for a certain amount thereafter.</p><p>When this occurs, characters will not be regarded as having experienced a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">defeat</span>. (Hence, their attached equipment and statuses will not be removed, and their Energy will remain uncleared.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/e810a8c5cbf997dc227fbf2bafa2512b_7499599974403109571.png",
                "id": "talent4353",
                "key": "Electro Crystal Core",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro Crystal Core"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">When this Summon is on the field</span>: Your opponent will have to spend 1 additional Elemental Die when performing \"Switch Character.\" (Once per Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_78992291876716093.png",
                "id": "talent43293",
                "key": "Chains of Warding Thunder",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/35428890/6f0d7b0b3f0cda9d42d38485a7202bcc_8384317384876139547.png",
                "title": "Chains of Warding Thunder"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_9133862142528888163.png",
                "id": "talent98437",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prepare Skill</span></strong></p><p>Some Skills cannot be used directly. Instead, they need to be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span> over a certain number of turns.<br>When it is a certain player's turn, and this player's active character is currently <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill, this player's turn will be skipped. If the Skill has finished being <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span>, the character will directly use that Skill at this time. (Skills that require <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> cannot activate effects triggered by \"using a Skill\" or \"triggering an Elemental Reaction\" or other such effects.)<br>Only active characters can <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepare</span> Skills, and if an active character who is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill gets switched off-field, their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparation</span> will be interrupted.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4975670166203916981.png",
                "id": "talent90637",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
